OL,4,C#2m blaze at Michelin-starred
OL,5,Crestaurant
OL,7,FA shooting estate manager accused of
OL,8,Fburning down a 14th century, Michelin-
OL,9,Fstarred restaurant, causing more than
OL,10,F#2 million of damage, has been told by
OL,11,Fa judge "you are not to blame for
OL,12,Fthis, you are perfectly innocent",
OL,13,Fafter the case against him was
OL,14,Fdropped.JCharlie Birkett, 28, was
OL,15,Fcharged with arson with recklessness
OL,16,Fas to whether property would be
OL,17,Fdestroyed or life endangered, after
OL,18,Fthe devastating blaze at the thatched
OL,19,FStar Inn at Harome, near Helmsley,
OL,20,FNorth Yorkshire, in November 2021.
