OL,3,CCase dropped against man accused of
OL,4,C#2m blaze at Michelin-starred
OL,5,Crestaurant
OL,7,FThe damage to the roof was significant.
OL,9,FAt York Crown Court on Friday,
OL,10,Fprosecutors offered no evidence, after
OL,11,Fthe production of a new report by one
OL,12,Fof Britain's leading fire
OL,13,Finvestigators, Dr Peter Mansi, which
OL,14,Fwas paid for by Mr Birkett's family,
OL,15,Fwho run the Rievaulx Sporting estate,
OL,16,Fin North Yorkshire.
