OL,3,CCase dropped against man accused of
OL,4,C#2m blaze at Michelin-starred
OL,5,Crestaurant
OL,7,FThe Recorder of York, Judge Sean
OL,8,FMorris, told Mr Birkett: "You are not
OL,9,Fto blame for this, you are perfectly
OL,10,Finnocent and you leave this court
OL,11,Fwithout a stain on your character."
OL,13,FThe court heard Mr Birkett was charged
OL,14,Fon the basis that he deliberately put
OL,15,Fa cigarette into the thatch of the
OL,16,Fbuilding.
