OL,7,FBut prosecutors admitted that Dr
OL,8,FMansi's new investigation showed that
OL,9,Fthis was not the case, and the fire
OL,10,Fwas caused by a candle in a makeshift
OL,11,Fashtray igniting cigarette butts,
OL,12,Fwhich spread to dead ivy around the
OL,13,Fdoor of the pub.
OL,15,FIn an emotional statement, Mr Birkett
OL,16,Fsaid his life has been "extremely
OL,17,Fhard" for the last two years as he
OL,18,Ffaced a possible prison term of more
OL,19,Fthan six years.
