OL,7,FThe inn was rebuilt and reopened on
OL,8,Fthe anniversary of the fire in 2022.
OL,9,FNo-one was injured in the blaze, and
OL,10,Fmore than 40 firefighters battled to
OL,11,Fsave the building.
OL,13,FSpeaking outside the court, Mr Birkett
OL,14,Fsaid: "I cannot quite describe the
OL,15,Flast two years and what myself, and
OL,16,Fthen my family and friends have been
OL,17,Fthrough."
