OL,7,FMr Birkett said: "I cannot thank
OL,8,FAndrew Pern (Owner, Star Inn) and his
OL,9,Ffamily enough, for all their kind
OL,10,Fwords and support.
OL,12,F"We are extremely close as families
OL,13,Fand were it not for his decency, his
OL,14,Fkindness and his knowledge of me and
OL,15,Fthat I would never have done what the
OL,16,Fpolice alleged, I think that this
OL,17,Fnegligent and flawed prosecution would
OL,18,Fhave ruined the relationship between
OL,19,Four families."
