OL,7,FHe said: "My worry is that there are
OL,8,Fother people out there under similar
OL,9,Fcircumstances who would not have had
OL,10,Fthe support, financially and
OL,11,Femotionally, that was needed to prove
OL,12,Fmy innocence. "
OL,14,FA CPS spokesperson said: "We have a
OL,15,Fduty to continually review cases, and
OL,16,Fafter receiving further expert
OL,17,Fevidence into the cause of the fire,
OL,18,Fwe concluded there was no longer a
OL,19,Frealistic prospect of conviction and
OL,20,Fstopped the case."
